**Overview**

This dashboard displays key statistics and visualizations based on policy audit event logs from the CyberArk EPM integration. It includes the top users, policies, products, and access targets; a breakdown of events by type, access target type, and source type; along with a time-based event trend line chart and essential details about policy audit event data.

[**Integration Page**](/app/integrations/detail/cyberark_epm/overview)
